item.title: SoftLayer_Event_Log
item.description: SoftLayer_Event_Log Service Datatype Description Event Log service lets you find interesting events related to various SoftLayer products and services such as hardware, virtual server or DNS. Methods getAllEventNames Return all indexed event names. getAllEventObjectNames Return all indexed event object names. getAllObjects Return the event log data getAllUserTypes Returns all possible event log user types getUser

item.title: SoftLayer_Event_Log
item.description: SoftLayer_Event_Log Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Event_Log data type contains an event detail occurred upon various SoftLayer resources. Local accountId Account id with which the event is associated Type: integer eventCreateDate Event creation date in millisecond precision Type: dateTime eventName Event name such as "reboot", "cancel", "update host" and so on. Type: string ipAddress The remote IP Address that made the request Type: string
